Package rubenchristoffer.hetty.codec

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    HTTPChunkedTransferDecoder
    HTTP Transfer Decoder that decodes body sent from server.
    HTTPChunkedTransferEncoder
    HTTP Transfer Decoder that encodes body sent to server.
    HTTPContentLengthTransferDecoder
    This is the default decoder used when decoding HTTP packets.
    HTTPTransferDecoder
    HTTP decoder responsible for decoding body when reading packet from server.
    HTTPTransferEncoder
    HTTP encoder that can encode body when sending packet
  • Enum Summary 
    Enum Description
    HTTPTransferDecoder.DecodeInfo
    Enum used for signalling the ability of this decoder to decode a packet.
  • Exception Summary

    Exception used when parts of the HTTP API encounters unsupported content.
